name: Fdlibm-js
tagline: A port of fdlibm to Javascript
body:
### fdlibm in Javascript
This is an implementation of Sun's [fdlibm](netlib.org/fdlibm) library of accurate special functions, ported to Javascript.

You set of tests (and special functions available) is at [test suite](rtoy.github.io/fdlibm-js/test-index.html)
